# AI Quote Comparison Service (AQCS)

## Product Vision

### Goal

Enable homeowners to upload one or more solar quotations and receive an AI-powered, unbiased comparison with actionable recommendations.

Unlike traditional comparison tables, the system should:

* Read quotations automatically
* Extract technical specifications
* Detect hidden risks
* Compare equipment quality
* Estimate long-term value
* Recommend the most suitable installer
* Explain every recommendation in natural language

The system should reinforce Solar AI Advisor's positioning as **India's Trusted AI Solar Advisor**, not just another lead-generation website.

